Class World

java.lang.Object

com.zanderwohl.chunks.World.World
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class World
extends Delta
implements java.io.Serializable
A collection of Volumes and their relations to each other, to allow for dynamic generation of the world in small pieces at a time. Contains other information.
